/gate/digitizer/Singles/insert thresholder
/gate/digitizer/Singles/thresholder/setThreshold 430. keV
/gate/digitizer/Singles/insert upholder
/gate/digitizer/Singles/upholder/setUphold 610. keV 

# DEAD TIME
